OL,4,G1800FTales Of The Unexpected
OL,5,     GThe Flypaper: Lorna Charles and
OL,6,     GAlfred Burke star in this twisted
OL,7,     Gtale. With a 12 year-old found
OL,8,     Gdead and a killer perhaps on the
OL,9,     Gloose, a young girl becomes
OL,10,     Gparanoid.
OL,11,G1830FTales Of The Unexpected
OL,12,     GThe Orderly World of Mr Appleby:
OL,13,     GRobert Lang stars in this tale
OL,14,     Gwith a twist. A man married three
OL,15,     Gtimes might be lucky for the
OL,16,     Gfourth time when he meets a new
OL,17,     Ginterest.
